Spezial Feature in vokoscreen.conf 

Path:
~/.config/vokoscreen/vokoscreen.conf

The entrys must be made with a text editor

[AREA]
# Introduced in vokoscreen 1.7.22 Beta
# Hide recordarea in Taskbar
NoShowInTaskBar=1 [Standard]

# Introduced in vokoscreen 1.7.22 Beta
# Show recordarea in Taskbar
NoShowInTaskBar=0
